OOC:

Actually it would.

Without the autobots the junkicons would have remained on their garbage scow
of a planet. The quints would remain on theirs. Unicron would devour
cybertron.

Maximals would cease to exist, predicons as well.

Simple rule of thumb: Never muck with the past, even killing a misquito in
the dino eras could result in the world being drastically altered.
